fields.name: VSL CALL ENGINE
fields.description: VSL Call Engine is a 2 funnel system that starts with a VSL and then disqualified leads go to a low ticket product

fields.name: Funnel Automation
fields.description: Funnel Automation is a 3 funnel system that is made to sell high ticket products, then disqualified leads go to a low ticket product.  The autowebinar is for leads that have not purchased and it will send them back to low ticket funnel.

fields.name: Digital Product Launchpad
fields.description: Digital Product Launchpad is one funnel to either get booked calls or sell a digital products.
